<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Welcome to Stellar Disbursement Platform</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        a {
            color: #3498db;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #3498db;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .button:hover {
            background-color: #3cb0fd;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <p>Hello, {{.FirstName}}!</p>
    <p>You have been added to your organization's Stellar Disbursement Platform as a {{.Role}}. Please click the link below to set up your password and let your organization administrator know if you have any questions.</p>
    <p>
        <a href="{{.ForgotPasswordLink}}" class="button">Set up my password</a>
    </p>
    <p>Best regards,</p>
    <p>The {{.OrganizationName}} Team</p>
</body>
</html>
